  "texts": [
    "The first variant is -VAE, which balances the capacity of the latent channels and the independence constraints, which describe the relations of the features decoded inside the latent space.",
    "Further architectural modifications such as Adversarial Autoencoder (AAE), two-stage VAEs, and hierarchical VAEs also exist.",
    "A method that is focused on generating new 2D images that are similar to existing images is called -VAE proposed by Higgins et al. (2017).",
    "The is a hyperparameter that is used to balance latent channel capacity and independence constraints while discovering more latent features.",
    "The drawback of this method is the dependence on the sampling density and the correct choice of."
  ]
